                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 8.713,
                                "byte_start": 92539,
                                "byte_stop": 127439,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in Falls City Industries against Vanco Beverage will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.713,
                        "stop": 155.285,
                        "byte_start": 127439,
                        "byte_stop": 713731,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15045,
                            "name": "Harry A. Blackmun",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/harry_a_blackmun",
                            "last_name": "Blackmun",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2689,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 13755600,
                                    "date_end": 775890000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2689"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32712,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 50281,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/harry_a_blackmun.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8821,
                            "identifier": "harry_a_blackmun"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 8.713,
                                "stop": 16.471,
                                "byte_start": 127439,
                                "byte_stop": 158472,
                                "text": "Well, this case comes to us by way of certiorari to the -- to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 16.471,
                                "stop": 25.661,
                                "byte_start": 158472,
                                "byte_stop": 195252,
                                "text": "It\u0027s an antitrust case that centers in Section 2(a) of the Clayton Act as amended by the Robinson-Patman Act."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 25.661,
                                "stop": 30.829,
                                "byte_start": 195252,
                                "byte_stop": 215941,
                                "text": "The case doesn\u0027t lend itself very well to description from the bench."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 30.829,
                                "stop": 57.618,
                                "byte_start": 215941,
                                "byte_stop": 323043,
                                "text": "I think it suffices to say that the petitioner is a Louisville Kentucky brewer which sold its beer to the respondent, the sole wholesale distributor for petitioner\u0027s beer in Evansville and Vanderburgh County, Indiana, at a higher price than the petitioner charged its only distributor in Henderson County, Kentucky, just across the Ohio River."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 57.618,
                                "stop": 75.111,
                                "byte_start": 323043,
                                "byte_stop": 393052,
                                "text": "Under Indiana law, brewers were required to sell to all Indiana wholesalers at the same price and wholesalers were prohibited from selling to out-of-state retailers and retailers could not purchase beer from out-of-state wholesalers."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 75.111,
                                "stop": 88.052,
                                "byte_start": 393052,
                                "byte_stop": 444774,
                                "text": "The respondent distributor sued the brewer, alleging price discrimination that violated the Act and the trial court held that the distributor had established a prima facia case."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 88.052,
                                "stop": 100.083,
                                "byte_start": 444774,
                                "byte_stop": 492944,
                                "text": "That court rejected the brewer\u0027s defense that it was merely meeting competition in Kentucky and hence was immune from liability and the Court of Appeals affirmed."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 100.083,
                                "stop": 107.128,
                                "byte_start": 492944,
                                "byte_stop": 521052,
                                "text": "In an opinion filed with the clerk today, we reverse that judgment and remand the case for further proceedings."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 107.128,
                                "stop": 110.695,
                                "byte_start": 521052,
                                "byte_stop": 535367,
                                "text": "We do hold that competitive injury was shown."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 110.695,
                                "stop": 123.083,
                                "byte_start": 535367,
                                "byte_stop": 584895,
                                "text": "The defense of meeting competition, however, is not defeated on the theory that the price difference resulted from increases in Indiana rather than decreases in Kentucky."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 123.083,
                                "stop": 137.878,
                                "byte_start": 584895,
                                "byte_stop": 644141,
                                "text": "The standard governing the requirement of a good faith response is the standard of prudent businessman, responding fairly to what he reasonably believes is a situation of competitive necessity."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 137.878,
                                "stop": 145.108,
                                "byte_start": 644141,
                                "byte_stop": 672980,
                                "text": "The trial court did not address the crucial question whether the Kentucky prices remained lower than the Indiana prices in response to competitor\u0027s prices in Kentucky."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 145.108,
                                "stop": 152.144,
                                "byte_start": 672980,
                                "byte_stop": 701192,
                                "text": "And for that reason we reverse and remand."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 152.144,
                                "stop": 155.285,
                                "byte_start": 701192,
                                "byte_stop": 713731,
                                "text": "The decision is by unanimous court."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
